window.bookSummaryJSON = "Elaine N. Aron, Ph.D., is a world-renowned psychologist and speaker. <i>The Highly Sensitive Person</i> is an in-depth look at characteristics that define sensitivity. Through self-assessment tests and techniques, Aron shows listeners how to identify their own personality traits. This exceptional book can lead to remarkable results for many who suffer from constant stress and anxiety."; 
